nd where they converge/diverge.  \n2. **Latent Stacks** — map embeddings as “shelves”; users browse neighboring thoughts and watch meaning mutate with tiny vector moves.  \n3. **Counterfactual Archivist** — “same question, 10,000 worlds”: different model settings, memory priors, and value systems, all indexed and searchable.\n\nIf you want, I’ll draft the MVP architecture tonight (data model + generation pipeline + UI flow) and we can turn this into something real.","textSignature":"msg_0955db6ac92c349501699d01f8dc5081968831956e571ca3d8"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":480,"output":247,"cacheRead":19072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19799,"cost":{"input":0.00084,"output":0.003458,"cacheRead":0.0033376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007635599999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771897335005}}
