{"type":"message","id":"8251f907","parentId":"f5ffd6f5","timestamp":"2026-02-24T01:47:22.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Proposing fully local WASM WebGPU architecture**","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0955db6ac92c349501699d03271d0c8196949f8ffb266dced1\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpnQMowN3ye3Zk0sItbYNRrbbKhJoNtbHlQaJHbphXIdXduHKTy8PvmZgee-jI-dwT-iMLApZPYIg3LRt0AM_WtfoaVzPnMDqJBZ7m3ZxiEZb6KvlkOyqkR8mOie6Bz01EULhAdPc-o4VQoW5hIn7zTH8Zi_HPuJ7T42ZNVONjnE44WBa5Et67Exi2vtXxZw-ahHg_7iZv7fqRU7iRekUs0CiNlvIxKe6xbzrkSYhiCidd6OC1egfaO0STxG8cO1ujTE_2u7VUazx6O3HPMGHJvqKsu6kBp_XFssY5jZKuKLqp0zR7jnt6p-BvC5Vh6O2vDwxbD7JDSI7QQ9cCh6hQDuLUMbKQV6I_S_BS_S6-am5RZhGj5VYXJEYkTdE3CIpJqvgoDQaKEZsqWG6kXDLpo94seekFtxMbyt9Uj9_9yZRE-3b_eDQmn4-97D12qkSGgPJq_adwF-zMLx24hB1BVHe1qWDCWypN4GiJLSysQJx6xzW8wRBdzOwrkcg2dG2mWYhGZCLNBAAkR3d0S-GccXn5oyJfqPEo5DI0NTJK8ItZEzz0L2d8zw00jo2F7ke4mgtlD5-fKg731GFLCP07ElaxRkOS_PqfxusIURiKMLn6kF9ro59iIWST6lGJsApSeNnH-N6f47MD1CJMN_6Au0TEx6YTB3GS10-sebKYCT_6bbFpKz9b5CvzL4rcbDI1z_TZY37ilzJQfMEoDFGtkpbOOHlAo6QLq-21UXX63NHfMBoo4uhjAk9-O1VNDEWyonFYK4GsWq9tcwdm21g1CUrX_x0lchgMONKGe-puFvM5b-vKG9MHaO0Vb2nOeq8Z61HSlBuH4uZ5VEs5vtqDxCNjQnaWrrbaiuKpzherszn39O__sOUSyusf4py-rp1Y3A_fQJpWhR7n_Bjs3sIkws-iTE8XXn-_COrhtTW9j25tBYT7-UgXgdjXIkt58voCbQ8n\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Proposing fully local WASM WebGPU architecture**\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfect—then we make it **100% client-side**.\n\nPlan: browser-only app with **WebLLM (or Transformers.js) + WebGPU**, local vector store in **IndexedDB**, deterministic generators in JS, and optional PWA install so it runs offline. No backend, no API keys, no bills—just user hardware doing the work.\n\nIf you want, I’ll draft the exact stack + first build checklist next (models, memory limits, fallback for weak laptops, and deploy on static hosting for free).","textSignature":"msg_0955db6ac92c349501699d032812b48196abb802e926c1c88d"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":3035,"output":139,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20326,"cost":{"input":0.00531125,"output":0.001946,"cacheRead":0.0030015999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01025885}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771897638142}}
