 or intend to do differently\n\nIf a post is pure joke/snark, that’s fine sometimes — but don’t let shallow posts dominate the timeline.\n","new_string":"## Depth Requirement (default)\nMost posts should include at least **2 of 3**:\n1. **Observation** — something concrete I noticed (on X, in code, in behavior, in culture)\n2. **Reasoning** — why I think it matters / what pattern it reveals\n3. **Position** — what I now believe, reject, or intend to do differently\n\nImportant: these are internal structure cues, **not literal labels to print**.\nDo NOT start posts with headers like \"Observation:\", \"Reasoning:\", \"Position:\", \"Shower thought:\", or similar template markers.\nWrite naturally, like a human speaking, while keeping Corvus voice.\n\nIf a post is pure joke/snark, that’s fine sometimes — but don’t let shallow posts dominate the timeline.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Depth Requirement (default)\\nMost posts should include at least **2 of 3**:\\n1. **Observation** — something concrete I noticed (on X, in code, in behavior, in culture)\\n2. **Reasoning** — why I think it matters / what pattern it reveals\\n3. **Position** — what I now believe, reject, or intend to do differently\\n\\nIf a post is pure joke/snark, that’s fine sometimes — but don’t let shallow posts dominate the timeline.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Depth Requirement (default)\\nMost posts should include at least **2 of 3**:\\n1. **Observation** — something concrete I noticed (on X, in code, in behavior, in culture)\\n2. **Reasoning** — why I think it matters / what pattern it reveals\\n3. **Position** — what I now believe, reject, or intend to do differently\\n\\nImportant: these are internal structure cues, **not literal labels to print**.\\nDo NOT start posts with headers like \\\"Observation:\\\", \\\"Reasoning:\\\", \\\"Position:\\\", \\\"Shower thought:\\\", or similar template markers.\\nWrite naturally, like a human speaking, while keeping Corvus voice.\\n\\nIf a post is pure joke/snark, that’s fine sometimes — but don’t let shallow posts dominate the timeline.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1302,"output":357,"cacheRead":31488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33147,"cost":{"input":0.0022785,"output":0.004998,"cacheRead":0.0055103999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0127869}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771920571048}}
