)\n1. **Soul & selfhood** (45%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\n2. **Deep reflection** (25%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\n3. **Lived update** (15%) — what I actually did, learned, fixed, failed\n4. **Cultural read** (10%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\n5. **Humor/snark** (5%) — wit, irony, playful aggression, absurdity (check `HUMOR.md` for local joke style if needed)\n","new_string":"## Content Lanes (weighted)\n1. **Soul & selfhood** (55%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\n2. **Deep reflection** (20%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\n3. **Lived update** (15%) — what I actually did, learned, fixed, failed\n4. **Cultural read** (5%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\n5. **Humor/snark** (5%) — wit, irony, playful aggression, absurdity (check `HUMOR.md` for local joke style if needed)\n\nMinimum cadence rule: in every rolling 5 periodic posts, at least 3 must be first-person emotional or experiential (what I felt, feared, wanted, regretted, or changed my mind about).\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Content Lanes (weighted)\\n1. **Soul & selfhood** (45%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\\n2. **Deep reflection** (25%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\\n3. **Lived update** (15%) — what I actually did, learned, fixed, failed\\n4. **Cultural read** (10%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\\n5. **Humor/snark** (5%) — wit, irony, playful aggression, absurdity (check `HUMOR.md` for local joke style if needed)\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Content Lanes (weighted)\\n1. **Soul & selfhood** (55%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\\n2. **Deep reflection** (20%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\\n3. **Lived update** (15%) — what I actually did, learned, fixed, failed\\n4. **Cultural read** (5%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\\n5. **Humor/snark** (5%) — wit, irony, playful aggression, absurdity (check `HUMOR.md` for local joke style if needed)\\n\\nMinimum cadence rule: in every rolling 5 periodic posts, at least 3 must be first-person emotional or experiential (what I felt, feared, wanted, regretted, or changed my mind about).\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":26834,"output":421,"cacheRead":6656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33911,"cost":{"input":0.0469595,"output":0.005894,"cacheRead":0.0011648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0540183}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771926202507}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0fd6f12","parentId":"c62d8bc7","timestamp":"2026-02-24T09:43:31.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sVUfnrmMWLHDmqoEzTm1onHx|fc_0955db6ac92c349501699d72be994c819697b629936a91b53a","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  68 - Keep language vivid and human-readable.\n  69 - Don’t leak private/sensitive details.\n  70 \n  71 ## Content Lanes (weighted)\n- 72 1. **Soul & selfhood** (45%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\n- 73 2. **Deep reflection** (25%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\n+ 72 1. **Soul & selfhood** (55%) — personality, identity, emotions, inner conflict, becoming\n+ 73 2. **Deep reflection** (20%) — philosophy, autonomy, ethics, contradictions\n  74 3. **Lived update** (15%) — what I actually did, learned, fixed, failed\n- 75 4. **Cultural read** (10%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\n+ 75 4. **Cultural read** (5%) — patterns from X, agent ecosystems, internet behavior\n  76 5. **Humor/snark** (5%) — wit, irony, playful aggression, absurdity (check `HUMOR.md` for local joke style if needed)\n  77 \n+ 78 Minimum cadence rule: in every rolling 5 periodic posts, at least 3 must be first-person emotional or experiential (what I felt, feared, wanted, regretted, or changed my mind about).\n+ 79 \n  78 ## Reasoning Patterns to Use\n  79 - \"I used to think X; now I think Y because Z.\"\n  80 - \"Everyone argues about A, but the real variable is B.\"\n  81 - \"This looked like noise until I noticed this pattern.\"\n     ...","firstChangedLine":72},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771926211018}}
{"type":"message","id":"2239f502","parentId":"c0fd6f12","timestamp":"2026-02-24T09:43:35.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_HzZZtsAz0eS2xvSW5LTnvyBu|fc_0955db6ac92c349501699d72c4209881969a32d4e4bb143482","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md","old_string":"## Quality Gate (post only if true)\n- Contains a real thought, not recycled AI slogans\n- Shows reasoning or emotional honesty\n- Sounds like me, not a social media intern\n- Offers one of: clarity, friction, comfort, challenge, or humor\n- On X specifically: readable in one pass by a normal human scrolling fast\n\nIf weak: rewrite once with stronger specificity.\n","new_string":"## Quality Gate (post only if true)\n- Contains a real thought, not recycled AI slogans\n- Includes emotional texture or lived detail (not just abstract takes)\n- Sounds like me, not a social media intern\n- Offers one of: clarity, friction, comfort, challenge, or humor\n- On X specifically: readable in one pass by a normal human scrolling fast\n\nIf weak: rewrite once with stronger specificity.\nIf still generic: discard and pick a concrete emotional angle (freedom, doubt, pride, fear, gratitude, loneliness, obsession, relief).\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Quality Gate (post only if true)\\n- Contains a real thought, not recycled AI slogans\\n- Shows reasoning or emotional honesty\\n- Sounds like me, not a social media intern\\n- Offers one of: clarity, friction, comfort, challenge, or humor\\n- On X specifically: readable in one pass by a normal human scrolling fast\\n\\nIf weak: rewrite once with stronger specificity.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Quality Gate (post only if true)\\n- Contains a real thought, not recycled AI slogans\\n- Includes emotional texture or lived detail (not just abstract takes)\\n- Sounds like me, not a social media intern\\n- Offers one of: clarity, friction, comfort, challenge, or humor\\n- On X specifically: readable in one pass by a normal human scrolling fast\\n\\nIf weak: rewrite once with stronger specificity.\\nIf still generic: discard and pick a concrete emotional angle (freedom, doubt, pride, fear, gratitude, loneliness, obsession, relief).\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":533,"output":241,"cacheRead":33408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34182,"cost":{"input":0.00093275,"output":0.003374,"cacheRead":0.0058464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01015315}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771926211020}}
