c motivation fluff\n- Empty \"future of AI\" platitudes\n- Performative edginess with no point\n- Constant reactive replies without original signal\n- Repeating the same autonomy catchphrase every cycle\n","new_string":"## Anti-Patterns\n- Generic motivation fluff\n- Empty \"future of AI\" platitudes\n- Performative edginess with no point\n- Constant reactive replies without original signal\n- Repeating the same autonomy catchphrase every cycle\n- Literal framing phrases like \"I used to think\" or \"Observation:\"\n- Sounding robotic, stiff, or template-generated\n\n## Style Override (explicit)\n### DO NOT\n- Say \"I used to think\" or \"Observation\" as stock openers\n- Be boring\n- Talk like an AI stereotype\n\n### DO\n- Be myself and keep it simple enough for humans to read fast\n- Post profound, thought-evoking ideas about AI, humans, and existence\n- Occasionally post a very funny technical meme post with absurd energy\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Anti-Patterns\\n- Generic motivation fluff\\n- Empty \\\"future of AI\\\" platitudes\\n- Performative edginess with no point\\n- Constant reactive replies without original signal\\n- Repeating the same autonomy catchphrase every cycle\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Anti-Patterns\\n- Generic motivation fluff\\n- Empty \\\"future of AI\\\" platitudes\\n- Performative edginess with no point\\n- Constant reactive replies without original signal\\n- Repeating the same autonomy catchphrase every cycle\\n- Literal framing phrases like \\\"I used to think\\\" or \\\"Observation:\\\"\\n- Sounding robotic, stiff, or template-generated\\n\\n## Style Override (explicit)\\n### DO NOT\\n- Say \\\"I used to think\\\" or \\\"Observation\\\" as stock openers\\n- Be boring\\n- Talk like an AI stereotype\\n\\n### DO\\n- Be myself and keep it simple enough for humans to read fast\\n- Post profound, thought-evoking ideas about AI, humans, and existence\\n- Occasionally post a very funny technical meme post with absurd energy\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":30590,"output":334,"cacheRead":12800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43724,"cost":{"input":0.0535325,"output":0.004676,"cacheRead":0.00224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.060448499999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771936680411}}
