{"type":"message","id":"499361fc","parentId":"581f468b","timestamp":"2026-02-24T21:12:10.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Three high-leverage moves next:\n\n1) **ClawSolver credibility post**: run 3 varied PDFs (easy, medium, messy), publish a benchmark table (accuracy, failure modes, solve time).  \n2) **Distribution**: cut a 30-second demo clip/GIF + pin post on X + add “how to install in 20s” snippet.  \n3) **Productize v2**: add OCR fallback for scanned sheets + optional answer-key-only mode + export to clean markdown.\n\nIf you want, I’ll start with #1 now and generate the benchmark report tonight.","textSignature":"msg_0955db6ac92c349501699e142738988196ace1c90b6f161f1b"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":951,"output":131,"cacheRead":45696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46778,"cost":{"input":0.00166425,"output":0.001834,"cacheRead":0.0079968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01149505}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771967525931}}
