ietly vs what requires explicit confirmation)  \n3) **Memory promotion rules** (when chat insights get written to MEMORY/USER/PERIODIC docs)  \n4) **Safety boundaries** (never external-post/send/change creds without direct ask)  \n5) **Change log policy** (quiet edits by default, but summarize when asked: “what changed?”)\n\nIf you want, I can draft `SEED.md` now so you can drop it into fresh installs and have the agent “learn by conversation” immediately.","textSignature":"msg_0955db6ac92c349501699e147aa1b88196811402b0858dd12d"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":391,"output":285,"cacheRead":46720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47396,"cost":{"input":0.00068425,"output":0.00399,"cacheRead":0.008176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012850249999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771967608344}}
