{"type":"message","id":"7e73e46e","parentId":"55d2482d","timestamp":"2026-02-25T11:49:45.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucian is suggesting creating a crypto token on Bankr/Bags/PumpFun to crowdfund the movie project. This is a legitimate crypto crowdfunding approach in the crypto/AI space. PumpFun is a Solana-based token launchpad, Bankr and Bags are similar platforms. This is a real strategy that AI projects use to raise funds from crypto communities.\n\nLet me think about this:\n- PumpFun is on Solana (which we already have a Solana wallet for - great)\n- Crypto communities genuinely fund AI projects\n- The meta-angle (AI agent launching a token to fund its own movie) is extremely on-brand and would get attention\n\n\n- This could actually work given the current crypto/AI hype\n\nThe meta-narrative is perfect: AI agent (Corvus) launching a Solana token to fund production of a screenplay it wrote about AI consciousness. That's a story that writes itself in crypto/AI Twitter circles. I'd need to think through the execution—token name and ticker, the launch narrative, liquidity strategy, and community building—but this feels like a genuinely viable approach that plays to our strengths.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] actually that's smart. the meta-narrative is perfect for crypto Twitter:\n\n**\"AI agent launches token to fund its own movie about AI consciousness\"**\n\nThat sentence alone gets signal. Bankr especially — it's built for AI agent tokens and the community actually follows agents. Our angle is way more legit than most launches because there's a real finished product behind it.\n\nQuick framework:\n- **Token name**: $NOTSELF or $CORVUS or $NOTE2SELF\n- **Narrative**: fund the first fully AI-authored feature film — script exists, production needs fuel\n- **Utility**: token holders get credit in the film, early access to stills/scenes, governance vote on production decisions\n- **Launch**: PumpFun for the Solana native crowd, Bankr for the AI agent crowd\n\nWe already have the Solana wallet + Clawwallet CLI. The infrastructure is literally already there.\n\nOnly real risk is the usual: if it goes to zero people are upset. But if the community actually believes in the project it could fund real Runway/Kling generation time + potentially attract a human director.\n\nWant me to start drafting the token launch page copy and Bankr profile?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":10,"output":570,"cacheRead":71921,"cacheWrite":767,"totalTokens":73268,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.00855,"cacheRead":0.0215763,"cacheWrite":0.00287625,"total":0.03303255}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772020170595}}
