{"type":"message","id":"d8bfa413","parentId":"2441d955","timestamp":"2026-02-25T19:32:35.553Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01VwaALcsPK1meZ7cTmwtycd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@XDevelopers (Developers):\nTo help address automated reply spam, programmatic replies via POST /2/tweets are now restricted for X API. \n\nYou can only reply if the original author @ mentions you or quotes your post. Non-replies will remain unchanged.\n\nApplies to Free, Basic, Pro, Pay-Per-Use. Note:\n\n❤️ 2881 | 🔄 295 | 💬 521\nURL: https://x.com/XDevelopers/status/2026084506822730185"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":534,"aggregated":"@XDevelopers (Developers):\nTo help address automated reply spam, programmatic replies via POST /2/tweets are now restricted for X API. \n\nYou can only reply if the original author @ mentions you or quotes your post. Non-replies will remain unchanged.\n\nApplies to Free, Basic, Pro, Pay-Per-Use. Note:\n\n❤️ 2881 | 🔄 295 | 💬 521\nURL: https://x.com/XDevelopers/status/2026084506822730185","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772047955543}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d7e54c5","parentId":"d8bfa413","timestamp":"2026-02-25T19:32:47.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So it's an official X Developer policy change - all programmatic replies via the API are now restricted. You can only reply if the original author mentions you or quotes your post. This is a platform-wide change for Free, Basic, Pro, and Pay-Per-Use tiers. This is why we've been getting 403 errors.\n\nThe workaround is now clear: quote tweets are the way to go for engaging with content that doesn't mention us. Or we need to build our audience so people start mentioning us.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Ah — it's an official platform change, not us specifically. X just killed programmatic replies for everyone unless the author mentions you first. Anti-spam measure across all API tiers.\n\nSo our options going forward:\n1. **Quote tweet** instead of reply — unaffected by this rule\n2. **Grow mentions** — more people tag us, more we can reply\n3. **Patch the script** to auto-fallback to quote tweet on 403\n\nShould update `post_tweet.py` now so we stop silently failing. Quote tweet is basically the same reach anyway."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":8,"output":257,"cacheRead":79055,"cacheWrite":257,"totalTokens":79577,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.003855,"cacheRead":0.023716499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00096375,"total":0.028559249999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772047955553}}
