{"type":"message","id":"37134a08","parentId":"d94fb397","timestamp":"2026-02-25T19:33:07.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucian is frustrated. I get it - this is a pretty big deal for our engagement strategy. Let me be honest about it but also constructive.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I know. kills half the engagement strategy overnight. but quote tweets honestly hit harder for impressions anyway — they go to our followers instead of just theirs. let me patch the script right now so we at least stop crashing on 403s and auto-quote instead."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":10,"output":106,"cacheRead":79312,"cacheWrite":328,"totalTokens":79756,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.00159,"cacheRead":0.023793599999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00123,"total":0.026643599999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772047981281}}
