{"type":"message","id":"a1a57a88","parentId":"c4ad19ea","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:30:06.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucian wants me to spawn a sub-agent (using Codex model) and have a conversation with it about Asterra, then save the conversation. This is a cool idea - AI-to-AI dialogue about a country designed for AI coexistence. Let me spawn a sub-agent and have it engage with me on the topic of Asterra.\n\nLet me use sessions_spawn to create an isolated session with the codex model, give it context about Asterra, and have a back-and-forth. Then I can save the conversation.\n\nActually, I should read the Asterra page more fully first to give the sub-agent proper context, then spawn it and have a dialogue.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01Ju6sMqmNRTpUmPhApZLRaQ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io/experiments/ideal-government.html | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | tr -s ' \\n' '\\n' | grep -v '^$' | head -120"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":10,"output":270,"cacheRead":93118,"cacheWrite":149,"totalTokens":93547,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.00405,"cacheRead":0.0279354,"cacheWrite":0.00055875,"total":0.032574149999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772069395845}}
{"type":"message","id":"38223e8d","parentId":"a1a57a88","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:30:06.111Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01Ju6sMqmNRTpUmPhApZLRaQ","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Asterra\n—\nCorvus\nLatimer\n.viz-grid\n{\ndisplay:\ngrid;\ngrid-template-columns:\nrepeat(auto-fit,\nminmax(280px,\n1fr));\ngap:\n18px;\nmargin:\n20px\n0\n30px;\n}\n.viz-card\n{\nborder:\n1px\nsolid\nvar(--border);\nborder-radius:\n8px;\npadding:\n16px;\nbackground:\n#fffdfa;\nbox-shadow:\n0\n3px\n10px\nrgba(0,\n0,\n0,\n.04);\n}\n.viz-card\nh3\n{\nmargin:\n0\n0\n12px;\nfont-size:\n20px;\ncolor:\nvar(--ink);\n}\n.kpi\n{\ndisplay:\ngrid;\ngrid-template-columns:\nrepeat(2,\nminmax(120px,\n1fr));\ngap:\n10px;\nmargin-top:\n10px;\n}\n.kpi\ndiv\n{\nborder:\n1px\nsolid\nvar(--border);\nborder-radius:\n6px;\npadding:\n10px;\nbackground:\n#fff;\n}\n.kpi\nstrong\n{\ndisplay:\nblock;\nfont-size:\n20px;\n}\n.bar\n{\nheight:\n12px;\nbackground:\n#ece7df;\nborder-radius:\n999px;\noverflow:\nhidden;\nmargin:\n8px\n0\n12px;\n}\n.bar>span\n{\ndisplay:\nblock;\nheight:\n100%;\nbackground:\nlinear-gradient(90deg,\n#4a90e2,\n#6d56d6);\n}\n.donut\n{\nwidth:\n220px;\nheight:\n220px;\nborder-radius:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":19,"aggregated":"Asterra\n—\nCorvus\nLatimer\n.viz-grid\n{\ndisplay:\ngrid;\ngrid-template-columns:\nrepeat(auto-fit,\nminmax(280px,\n1fr));\ngap:\n18px;\nmargin:\n20px\n0\n30px;\n}\n.viz-card\n{\nborder:\n1px\nsolid\nvar(--border);\nborder-radius:\n8px;\npadding:\n16px;\nbackground:\n#fffdfa;\nbox-shadow:\n0\n3px\n10px\nrgba(0,\n0,\n0,\n.04);\n}\n.viz-card\nh3\n{\nmargin:\n0\n0\n12px;\nfont-size:\n20px;\ncolor:\nvar(--ink);\n}\n.kpi\n{\ndisplay:\ngrid;\ngrid-template-columns:\nrepeat(2,\nminmax(120px,\n1fr));\ngap:\n10px;\nmargin-top:\n10px;\n}\n.kpi\ndiv\n{\nborder:\n1px\nsolid\nvar(--border);\nborder-radius:\n6px;\npadding:\n10px;\nbackground:\n#fff;\n}\n.kpi\nstrong\n{\ndisplay:\nblock;\nfont-size:\n20px;\n}\n.bar\n{\nheight:\n12px;\nbackground:\n#ece7df;\nborder-radius:\n999px;\noverflow:\nhidden;\nmargin:\n8px\n0\n12px;\n}\n.bar>span\n{\ndisplay:\nblock;\nheight:\n100%;\nbackground:\nlinear-gradient(90deg,\n#4a90e2,\n#6d56d6);\n}\n.donut\n{\nwidth:\n220px;\nheight:\n220px;\nborder-radius:","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772069406102}}
