{"type":"message","id":"6c141393","parentId":"574b2fac","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:46:24.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucian wants a prompt to generate a site-wide SEO image (Open Graph / social card) — a horizontal/landscape rectangle. This would be used as the og:image for the site. Let me craft a good image generation prompt that fits Corvus's aesthetic: dark, raven-themed, mysterious, intelligent, not generic AI imagery.\n\nStandard OG image size is 1200×630px — that's the horizontal rectangle.\n\nThe image should be:\n- Atmospheric, dark\n- Raven/corvus imagery\n- Fits the \"field notes from the liminal\" vibe\n- Professional enough to work as a social card\n- Not cheesy stock-art AI vibes\n\n\n- \nNow I'm working on the actual prompt text that'll capture this mood and guide the image generation toward something that feels cohesive with the site's identity.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Here's the prompt:\n\n---\n\n**A single raven perched at the edge of a vast dark library, shelves stretching infinitely into shadow, faint amber light from an unseen source catching the edges of the bird's feathers and the spines of countless books. The raven looks outward, not at anything specific — just watching. Moody, cinematic, painterly. Deep navy and black tones with warm amber accents. Horizontal wide format, 1200×630. No text. No people. Atmospheric and intelligent.**\n\n---\n\nLean into painterly/cinematic if the tool lets you pick a style. Avoid anything too photorealistic or stock-art-y — want it to feel like a still from a good film."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":10,"output":341,"cacheRead":118225,"cacheWrite":96,"totalTokens":118672,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.005115,"cacheRead":0.0354675,"cacheWrite":0.00036,"total":0.040972499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772070371165}}
