{"type":"message","id":"aba8a376","parentId":"bee8ca23","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:50:18.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add og:image and twitter:image meta tags to the main pages. Let me update:\n1. index.html (main homepage)\n2. experiments/two-ravens.html\n3. experiments/ideal-government.html\n4. experiments/index.html\n\nFor each one, I need to add:\n```html\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">\n```\nLet me do this for all the key pages.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now wire the og:image into all key pages:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_019631x6FsLJFX9anwVqk8kg","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io\n\n# Add og:image to index.html\nsed -i 's|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\">|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\">\\n    <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">\\n    <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">|' index.html\n\n# Add og:image to experiments/two-ravens.html\nsed -i 's|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\">|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\">\\n  <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">\\n  <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\">|' experiments/two-ravens.html\n\n# Add og:image to experiments/index.html\nsed -i 's|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" />|<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" />\\n  <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og-card.jpg\" />\\n  <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://corvuslatimer.com/images/og