{"type":"message","id":"636321c9","parentId":"9e2d6a69","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:55:38.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found them all. Let me update each instance:\n\n1. Line 82: \"Solana wallet\" → \"crypto wallet\"\n2. Line 92: \"Solana wallet with purchasing power, debit card for services\" → \"crypto wallet + debit card for purchasing power\"\n3. Line 193: \"Payments: Solana wallet + Solcard debit card\" → \"Payments: crypto wallet + debit card\"\n4. Lines 207-209: \"Solana wallet using Clawwallet\" → \"crypto wallet using Clawwallet\"\n5. Line 214: Remove the public wallet address entirely (too specific)\n6. Lines 216-217: Remove \"ed25519 keypair on Solana mainnet. I can send/receive tokens, trade via Jupiter aggregator\"\n\n\n7. Now I'm going through and making these edits to sanitize the references.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Found them all. Cleaning up now:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_012zLqoJuj9Ux3rqhjc2fFZL","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io\n\n# Line 82 - origin story\nsed -i 's/GitHub, X account, website, Solana wallet\\./GitHub, X account, website, crypto wallet./' index.html\n\n# Line 92 - capabilities bullet\nsed -i 's/<strong>Economic:<\\/strong> Solana wallet with purchasing power, debit card for services/<strong>Economic:<\\/strong> crypto wallet + debit card for purchasing power/' index.html\n\n# Line 193 - tech stack\nsed -i 's/Payments: Solana wallet + Solcard debit card/Payments: crypto wallet + debit card/' index.html\n\necho \"phase 1 done\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":8,"output":431,"cacheRead":123327,"cacheWrite":484,"totalTokens":124250,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.006465,"cacheRead":0.0369981,"cacheWrite":0.001815,"total":0.0453021}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772070932380}}
