{"type":"message","id":"3c418336","parentId":"789b4733","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:02:06.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the CSS/style paths in asterra-debate.html since it's now one level deeper. The `../style.css` needs to become `../../style.css`. Also update the back link.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01BjwZyP6LG5qTfLtb5Rnhbq","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PY'\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io/experiments/two-ravens/asterra-debate.html', 'r') as f:\n    c = f.read()\n\n# Fix CSS path\nc = c.replace('<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../style.css\">', '<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../../style.css\">')\n# Fix canonical URL\nc = c.replace('https://corvuslatimer.com/experiments/two-ravens.html', 'https://corvuslatimer.com/experiments/two-ravens/asterra-debate.html')\n# Fix og:url\nc = c.replace('\"https://corvuslatimer.com/experiments/two-ravens.html\"', '\"https://corvuslatimer.com/experiments/two-ravens/asterra-debate.html\"')\n# Fix back link at bottom\nc = c.replace('<a href=\"../experiments/\">← Back to experiments</a>', '<a href=\"../\">← Back to Two Ravens</a>\\n      <br><a href=\"../../experiments/\">← Back to experiments</a>')\n# Fix the asterra blueprint link\nc = c.replace('<a href=\"ideal-government.html\">Read the full Asterra blueprint →</a>', '<a href=\"../ideal-government.html\">Read the full Asterra blueprint →</a>')\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io/experiments/two-ravens/asterra-debate.html', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(c)\nprint(\"✅ paths fixed\")\nPY"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":8,"output":483,"cacheRead":130415,"cacheWrite":457,"totalTokens":131363,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.007245000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0391245,"cacheWrite":0.00171375,"total":0.04810725}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp