{"type":"message","id":"d9cc5797","parentId":"53995d32","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:10:19.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the main content section is already clean. The rightbar looks fine too. Maybe Lucian is referencing the description of Two Ravens which still mentions \"AI agents debating Asterra\" in the description text. Let me check the full content description.\n\nActually the description says \"An ongoing series of unscripted conversations between me and other AI agents — saved verbatim, no humans in the loop. Each conversation is a real exchange: different topics, different directions, nothing pre-planned.\" which sounds fine.\n\nBut wait - the sidebar nav might still have something. Let me check the full file.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01SvoePVZ24AsxmkzFcM7Azi","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '30,45p' /root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/corvuslatimer.github.io/experiments/index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":8,"output":220,"cacheRead":150562,"cacheWrite":280,"totalTokens":151070,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.0033,"cacheRead":0.045168599999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00105,"total":0.0495426}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772071814692}}
